parameters:
Warrior from Iremo Village: Outsiders bring disaster, I want
you to leave immediately.

Thanks to all of you who saved the village chief and the
priestess of the Iremo Village, we are grateful.

Thanks to all of you who saved the village chief and the
priestess of the Iremo Village, we are grateful.
Mage Relm: That was such a gloomy atmosphere!
Thief Nora: R-Relm-san!? Your voice is so loud...!

Priestess Sophia: It seems like she didn't approve of being
connected to the outside. It might be best to finish quickly
and leave.
Clea: Yes, I think that would be a good idea.

The warrior of Iremo Village: The beasts have been escaping
to the entrance of the village. I want you to repel them all
and exterminate them.

Warrior of Iremo Village: I don't want unnecessary
conversations with outsiders like you. I want you to defeat
them and leave immediately.
Warrior of Iremo Village: Let me know when you're ready.

Warrior of Iremo Village: It looks like we're ready. Stay on
guard, they're about to attack!
Clea: This is the end, isn't it?

Warrior of Iremo Village: Report to Village Chief Olden for
a job well done and then leave immediately.

Mage Relm: Sigh... It's such a terrible treatment. If a mage
from the Magic Academy were to come, there would be a big
commotion.
Warrior of Iremo Village: ...the Magic Academy

Mage Relm: Yes, I am a mage from the Magic Academy! It's
great that you get to talk to a genius like me.

Priestess Sophia: It seems like something has changed,
doesn't it?

Thief Nora: The animals we fought seemed to be scared of
something, and the people in this village also seem to be
afraid of something...?

Village Chief Olden: I apologize for causing trouble to all
of you. I couldn't protect my daughter or uphold the oath
with our ancestors.

Village Chief Olden: Please do as you wish with the voice
magic that has been passed down in our clan, whether you
sell it or use it.

Mage Relm: I-I've made an incredible discovery and
achievement! It's a major breakthrough that confirms my
status as an advanced sorcerer at the academy!

Clea: Regarding that matter, how about we request the guild
to keep it a secret?
Mage Relm: W-Wait, wait a minute, Clea-san!?

Clea: If you request it, the guild will definitely keep
everyone's secret.

Village Chief Olden: Why are you going to such lengths for
us?

Clea: My father was killed by a dragon, but you're still
alive, and Phoni-san is alive too.

Clea: If we're both alive, I don't mind taking it slowly. I
just want us to come together.
Clea: This is the condition for accepting the request.

Village Chief Olden: ...I appreciate your proposal. I will
formally request the Adventurer's Guild for assistance.
Village Chief Olden: Phoni... Let's go home.

Mage Relm: Why are you meddling?! This was my chance to get
promoted!!

Clea: If it's Relm-san, it should be fine. As a genius mage,
she should be able to handle it on her own.

Priestess Sophia: Oh my, I suppose this is Clea-chan's
victory, isn't it?

Mage Relm: Grumble... Fine, if my genius is recognized, then
so be it!

Thief Nora: You've gotten closer to the dragon! But we still
don't know its whereabouts.

Clea: Let's ask Phoni-san. She might have some hints about
its whereabouts.

Voice Priestess Phoni: Ah, it was all of you. I couldn't
calm down with everyone inside the house...
Voice Priestess Phoni: I apologize for involving all of you.

Clea: Could you please tell us what you know about the
whereabouts of the dragon?

Voice Priestess Phoni: I spent about a month with the
dragon. Its body was terribly damaged, and it remained still
like a rock.

Voice Priestess Phoni: The dragon seemed to be resting its
body quietly without touching any food or me.

Voice Priestess Phoni: And then one day, it suddenly
disappeared into the sky. I'm sorry, but I don't know where
it went.

Clea: Thank you very much. Just knowing that it is alive is
enough.

Voice Priestess Phoni: Clea-san's father was killed by the
dragon.

Clea: Not just my father, but my mother as well. The dragon
took everything away from me.

Clea: I became an adventurer in order to seek revenge
against the dragon.

Voice Priestess Phoni: Will I... be able to live happily
with my father again?

Clea: It's okay, even if it's not right away, there should
definitely be time for the two of us...

Voice Priestess Phoni: Thank you very much. If Clea-san ever
needs help, please don't hesitate to reach out to me.

Voice Priestess Phoni: There may not be much I can do, but I
will definitely cooperate for the sake of your goal!

Clea: Yes, thank you very much. If that time comes, I will
definitely reach out to you.

Voice Priestess Phoni: Yes! That's right, if you're okay
with it, please take this!

Voice Priestess Phoni: I may not have much to offer, but I
will definitely cooperate for the sake of your objective!
Voice Priestess Phoni: Clea-san, is something the matter?

Clea: Actually, I would like to ask for Phoni-san's
cooperation. Would it be possible for you to come with me to
the Valier region?
Voice Priestess Phoni: Of course, everyone is my savior!

Voice Priestess Phoni: This is my first time leaving here,
so I'm looking forward to it.

Voice Priestess Phoni: During the journey, I will be with
Clea-san... so...
Clea: Huh, yes, we'll be together, right?
Thief Nora: Look, Relm-san! The lilies are blooming!
Mage Relm: It's not that unusual, you know...

Priestess Sophia: Oh my, it seems that lilies are blooming
over there as well.
Thief Nora: Huh, where is it!?

Mage Relm: It's just a drunken hallucination... Let's
quickly join up with Armada-san.
Farmer Man: ...Sorry, but I can't talk to outsiders.
Farmer Man: Thank you for saving the shrine maiden, m'lady.
Farmer Man: ...Sorry, but I can't talk to outsiders.
Farmer's Wife: Thank you for saving Lady Phoni.
Silent Old Woman: ...I just want to be left alone.

Silent Old Woman: The shrine maiden has returned...! Our
prayers have reached the goddess Imiserinos!
Village Child: Thank you for saving Lady Phoni!
Voice Priestess Phoni: Everyone, thank you for coming!

Clea: Actually, I came here with something to discuss, and
Phoni-san's face came to mind first.
Voice Priestess Phoni: First and foremost... I am needed...!

Clea: I thought that only Phoni-san could be relied upon for
this.
Voice Priestess Phoni: Only Clea-san... hehehe...

Voice Priestess Phoni: I-if there's anything I can do...
please leave it to me!

Mage Relm: ...Clea-san, you have a tendency to misunderstand
things, don't you?

Priestess Sophia: Clea-chan is troublesome because she's
unaware of it.

Thief Nora: Please be careful of the lilies at your feet!
The captain said that something bad will happen if you walk
through the lilies!
Voice Priestess Phoni: The dragon is at Mount Monimos...!

Clea: Yes, it's the dragon that Phoni-san encountered, and
the one who killed my parents is there.

Clea: It seems that goblins and orcs are gathering, possibly
due to the influence of the dragon.

Voice Priestess Phoni: Understood... I might be able to
neutralize the goblins with my voice magic.

Voice Priestess Phoni: I will definitely go too! Not just
for Clea-san, but as the duty of a Voice Priestess.

Voice Priestess Phoni: The dragon destroyed the relationship
between me and my father. If we can defeat the dragon...
will things go back to how they were?

Clea: There's no need to worry, there's no parent and child
who would worry about such things.
Voice Priestess Phoni: Yes... Thank you very much!

Voice Priestess Phoni: I want to personally inform my father
about going to defeat the dragon... face to face.

Clea: Are there any other people who seem like they could be
of help in battle...?

Mage Relm: What about Opro-san? The Goblin Slayer will
definitely be a valuable asset in battle!

Thief Nora: What about Armada-san? Also, Goat-san seemed to
have a strong scent!

Priestess Sophia: What about Cors-san? That person might
know some strong mercenaries, regardless of their own
strength.
Clea: It might be worth trying to negotiate.
暗闇治療のハーブを所有していない場合

Man in black: ...It seems that the request has not been
fulfilled. Please come back here with the herbs for treating
darkness.
Clea: Are you Book-san, the client?

Man in black: I am the agent. Shall I give you what was
promised?

Man in black: Indeed, I have received it... Here is your
reward.

Man in black: My mission is complete. The client is inside
the building, so please make contact.

Clea: Why is the agent here when the client is inside the
building?

Clea: It seems better to be cautious. There is a possibility
of some kind of trap emerging.
Priestess Sophia: Yes, we need to make sure.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
Voice Priestess Phoni: Clea, what's wrong today?

Clea: Actually, I've come to make a really troublesome
request.

Voice Priestess Phoni: A new dragon... such a thing in the
royal palace...!

Clea: There might be other monsters besides dragons. I would
like to borrow the power of voice magic, if possible.

Voice Priestess Phoni: I was taught not to get deeply
involved with people outside the village, but Clea and the
others have completely shattered that value system.

Voice Priestess Phoni: I don't know if Clea and the others'
choice is right for the empire.

Voice Priestess Phoni: But you know, as I mentioned before,
no matter what happens, I will always be on Clea's side.

Clea: Actually, I was hesitant about reaching out this time.
This mission is clearly more dangerous than the previous
dragon subjugation.
Clea: If my thoughts change, I will contact the guild--

Voice Priestess Phoni: You helped me! It should prove that
we can adventure and fight together.

Voice Priestess Phoni: So, don't say such lonely things...
Clea.

Voice Priestess Phoni: If there is anything I can do for
Clea, just as Clea has become a strength for me, I want to
help.

Voice Priestess Phoni: If the threat of dragons and monsters
is looming over the people, then my power is meant for the
sake of the people.

Voice Priestess Phoni: I will cooperate with Clea. That is
the new way of being a priestess for me.
Clea: Hehe, you've become really reliable, haven't you?
Voice Priestess Phoni: Yes, it's thanks to everyone.

Clea: Let's fight together, for the people living in the
empire.

Voice Priestess Phoni: Yes, please let me fight together
with you.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
